      <title>调查显示，特朗普总统是东南亚的主要关注点。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-presidency-a-key-concern-for-southeast-asia-survey-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统今年重返白宫，在一项新调查中被确定为东南亚前三名地缘政治担忧之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-presidency-a-key-concern-for-southeast-asia-survey-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 05:35:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国因涉嫌间谍而拘留三个菲律宾人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/china-detains-three-filipinos-for-alleged-spying-as-ties-fray</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，它拘留了三名涉嫌间谍的菲律宾国民，这一举动可能会进一步构成北京和马尼拉之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/china-detains-three-filipinos-for-alleged-spying-as-ties-fray</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:58:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的“互惠”关税配方与贸易赤字有关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-reciprocal-tariff-formula-is-all-about-trade-deficits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的政府主要根据现有的贸易余额＆Mdash计算了其新的新关税。与其他国家 /地区的关税利率和其他贸易障碍相匹配的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-reciprocal-tariff-formula-is-all-about-trade-deficits</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:25:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Le Pen的法律命运从一个山区的副市长骑行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/marine-le-pen-appeal-bid-lies-in-hands-of-lawyer-rodolphe-bosselut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在法国法律界，有一群紧密编织的杰出的白领 - 犯罪律师，他们是尼古拉斯·萨科齐（Nicolas Sarkozy）到瑞士银行庞然大物瑞银集团AG的备受瞩目的被告的磁铁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/marine-le-pen-appeal-bid-lies-in-hands-of-lawyer-rodolphe-bosselut</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:00:16 GMT</pubDate>
